==Yin Earth Goat (己未)'s Months==
In a {{ill|Western calendar|ja|西暦}} year whose final digit is 3 or 8 (when the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|ja|十干}} are {{ill|Gui|ja|癸|1=Mizunoto (癸)}} or {{ill|Bo|ja|戊|1=Tsuchinoe (戊)}}), the month of {{ill|June|ja|6月}} is designated as the {{ill|month (calendar)|ja|月 (暦)}} of {{ill|Kibi|ja|己未}}. However, here the term "month" may refer either to the month of the {{ill|Lunisolar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar}} or to the {{ill|Seasonal Month|ja|節月}} (from {{ill|Minor Heat|ja|小暑}} until the day before {{ill|Beginning of Autumn|ja|立秋}}) as applicable.

==Yin Earth Goat (己未)'s Days==
The {{ill|selected day|ja|選日|1=Senjitsu}} for {{ill|Kibi|ja|己未}} is as follows.
=== Selected Day (選日) ===
The day of {{ill|Kibi|ja|己未}} is the 5th day of {{ill|Hassen|ja|八専}} (excluding gap days).



