==Yin Earth Goat (己未)'s Months==
In a {{ill|Western calendar|ja|西暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} year whose final digit is 3 or 8 (when the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|ja|十干|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} are {{ill|Gui|ja|癸|1=Mizunoto (癸)|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} or {{ill|Bo|ja|戊|1=Tsuchinoe (戊)|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}), the month of {{ill|June|ja|6月|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} is designated as the {{ill|month (calendar)|ja|月 (暦)|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} of {{ill|Kibi|ja|己未|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}. However, here the term "month" may refer either to the month of the {{ill|Lunisolar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} or to the {{ill|Seasonal Month|ja|節月|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (from {{ill|Minor Heat|ja|小暑|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} until the day before {{ill|Beginning of Autumn|ja|立秋|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) as applicable.

==Yin Earth Goat (己未)'s Days==
The {{ill|selected day|ja|選日|1=Senjitsu|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} for {{ill|Kibi|ja|己未|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} is as follows.
=== Selected Day (選日) ===
The day of {{ill|Kibi|ja|己未|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} is the 5th day of {{ill|Hassen|ja|八専|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (excluding gap days).
