It is the 56th combination of the {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|六十干支|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, preceded by {{ill|Bokugo|ja|戊午|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} and followed by {{ill|Koushin|ja|庚申|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}. In the framework of {{ill|Yin Yang Five Elements Thought|ja|陰陽五行思想|1=Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|ja|十干|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} symbol {{ill|Ki|ja|己|1=Tsuchinoto (己)|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} represents yin {{ill|Earth|ja|土|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, and the {{ill|Earthly Branches|ja|十二支|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} symbol {{ill|Goat|ja|未|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} represents yin {{ill|Earth|ja|土|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, forming a harmonious relationship ({{ill|Hiwa|ja|比和|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}).

==Yin Earth Goat (己未)'s Years==
A year in the {{ill|Western calendar|ja|西暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} that leaves a remainder of 59 when divided by 60 is a {{ill|year|ja|年|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} of {{ill|Kibi|ja|己未|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}.
