==Yin Earth Goat (己未)'s Years== A year in the [[:en:Common Era|Common Era]] that leaves a remainder of 59 when divided by 60 is a [[:en:Year|year]] of {{ill|Kibi|ja|1=Yin Earth Goat|2=ja|己未|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kibi|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kibi|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Earth Goat|qq=}}. {| class="wikitable" |+'''Yin Earth Goat (己未)'s years table''' |- ! [[:en:1st millennium|1st Millennium]] !! [[:en:2nd millennium|2nd Millennium]] !! [[:en:3rd millennium|3rd Millennium]] |- | * [[:en:AD 59|59 AD]] * [[:en:AD 119|119 AD]] * [[:en:179|179 AD]] * [[:en:239|239 AD]] * [[:en:299|299 AD]] * [[:en:359|359 AD]] * [[:en:419|419 AD]] * [[:en:479|479 AD]] * [[:en:539|539 AD]] * [[:en:599|599 AD]] * [[:en:659|659 AD]] * [[:en:719|719 AD]] * [[:en:779|779 AD]] * [[:en:839|839 AD]] * [[:en:899|899 AD]] * [[:en:959|959 AD]] | * [[:en:1019|1019 AD]] * [[:en:1079|1079 AD]] * [[:en:1139|1139 AD]] * [[:en:1199|1199 AD]] * [[:en:1259|1259 AD]] * [[:en:1319|1319 AD]] * [[:en:1379|1379 AD]] * [[:en:1439|1439 AD]] * [[:en:1499|1499 AD]] * [[:en:1559|1559 AD]] * [[:en:1619|1619 AD]] * [[:en:1679|1679 AD]] * [[:en:1739|1739 AD]] * [[:en:1799|1799 AD]] * [[:en:1859|1859 AD]] * [[:en:1919|1919 AD]] * [[:en:1979|1979 AD]] | * {{ill|2039 AD|ja|2039年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2039|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2039 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2099 AD|ja|2099年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2099|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2099 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2159 AD|ja|2159年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2159|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2159 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2219 AD|ja|2219年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2219|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2219 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2279 AD|ja|2279年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2279|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2279 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2339 AD|ja|2339年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Im