==Pronunciation== ==Years of Yin Earth Goat== A year in the [[:en:Common Era|Common Era]] that leaves a remainder of 59 when divided by 60 is a [[:en:Year|year]] of {{ill|Kibi|ja|1=Yin Earth Goat|2=ja|己未|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kibi|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kibi|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Earth Goat|qq=}}. {| class="wikitable" |+'''Yin Earth Goat (己未)'s years table''' |- ! [[:en:1st millennium|1st Millennium]] !! [[:en:2nd millennium|2nd Millennium]] !! [[:en:3rd millennium|3rd Millennium]] |- | * [[:en:AD 59|59 AD]] * [[:en:AD 119|119 AD]] * [[:en:179|179 AD]] * [[:en:239|239 AD]] * [[:en:299|299 AD]] * [[:en:359|359 AD]] * [[:en:419|419 AD]] * [[:en:479|479 AD]] * [[:en:539|539 AD]] * [[:en:599|599 AD]] * [[:en:659|659 AD]] * [[:en:719|719 AD]] * [[:en:779|779 AD]] * [[:en:839|839 AD]] * [[:en:899|899 AD]] * [[:en:959|959 AD]] | * [[:en:1019|1019 AD]] * [[:en:1079|1079 AD]] * [[:en:1139|1139 AD]] * [[:en:1199|1199 AD]] * [[:en:1259|1259 AD]] * [[:en:1319|1319 AD]] * [[:en:1379|1379 AD]] * [[:en:1439|1439 AD]] * [[:en:1499|1499 AD]] * [[:en:1559|1559 AD]] * [[:en:1619|1619 AD]] * [[:en:1679|1679 AD]] * [[:en:1739|1739 AD]] * [[:en:1799|1799 AD]] * [[:en:1859|1859 AD]] * [[:en:1919|1919 AD]] * [[:en:1979|1979 AD]] | * {{ill|2039 AD|ja|2039年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2039|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2039 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2099 AD|ja|2099年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2099|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2099 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2159 AD|ja|2159年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2159|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2159 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2219 AD|ja|2219年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2219|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2219 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2279 AD|ja|2279年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2279|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2279 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2339 AD|ja|2339年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2339|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2339 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2399 AD|ja|2399年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2399|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2399 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2459 AD|ja|2459年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2459|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2459 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2519 AD|ja|2519年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2519|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2519 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2579 AD|ja|2579年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2579|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2579 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2639 AD|ja|2639年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2639|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2639 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2699 AD|ja|2699年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2699|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2699 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2759 AD|ja|2759年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2759|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2759 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2819 AD|ja|2819年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2819|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2819 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2879 AD|ja|2879年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2879|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2879 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2939 AD|ja|2939年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2939|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2939 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2999 AD|ja|2999年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2999|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2999 AD|qq=}} |}
==Months of Yin Earth Goat== In a [[:en:Common Era|Common Era]] year whose final digit is 3 or 8 (when the [[:en:Heavenly Stems|Heavenly Stems]] are {{ill|Gui|ja|癸|1=Mizunoto (癸)|lt=Mizunoto (癸)|2=ja|3=癸|4=zh|5=癸|1=Mizunoto (癸)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gui|13=User:Immanuelle/Mizunoto (癸)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gui|13=User:Immanuelle/Mizunoto (癸)|qq=}} or {{ill|Bo|ja|戊|1=Tsuchinoe (戊)|lt=Tsuchinoe (戊)|2=ja|3=戊|4=zh|5=戊|1=Tsuchinoe (戊)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Bo|13=User:Immanuelle/Tsuchinoe (戊)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Bo|13=User:Immanuelle/Tsuchinoe (戊)|qq=}}), the month of [[:en:June|June]] is designated as the [[:en:Month|month (calendar)]] of {{ill|Kibi|ja|1=Yin Earth Goat|2=ja|己未|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kibi|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kibi|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Earth Goat|qq=}}. However, here the term "month" may refer either to the month of the {{ill|Lunisolar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lunisolar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lunisolar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}} or to the [[:en:Solar term|Solar term]] (from [[:en:Xiaoshu|Minor Heat]] until the day before [[:en:Liqiu|Beginning of Autumn]]) as applicable.
==Days of Yin Earth Goat== The {{ill|selected day|ja|選日|1=Senjitsu|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/selected day|13=User:Immanuelle/Senjitsu|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/selected day|13=User:Immanuelle/Senjitsu|qq=}} for {{ill|Kibi|ja|1=Yin Earth Goat|2=ja|己未|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kibi|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kibi|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Earth Goat|qq=}} is as follows. === Selected Day (選日) === The day of {{ill|Kibi|ja|1=Yin Earth Goat|2=ja|己未|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kibi|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kibi|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Earth Goat|qq=}} is the 5th day of {{ill|Hassen|ja|八専|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hassen|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hassen|qq=}} (excluding gap days). ==See Also== *{{prefix|qq=}} *{{intitle|qq=}}
