==Pronunciation== * Yin Earth Goat (己未) ** Chinese (Mandarin Pinyin): jǐwèi ** Cantonese (Jyutping): gei2 mei6 ** Japanese: ***Kunyomi: つちのとひつじ (tsuchinoto-hitsuji) ***Onyomi: きかのひつじ (kika-no-hitsuji) ***Onyomi: きび (kibi) ** Korean (Revised Romanization): gimi ** Vietnamese (Hán-Việt): Kỷ Mùi
